nt-size:var(--std-intro-size);color:var(--text2);line-height:1.65;font-weight:300\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e\">Six core modules that cover the complete commercial relationship — from the first SOR to the last audit entry.</p></div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e s5-feature-grid\"><div style=\"background:var(--navy);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 26px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;cursor:default;transition:all .35s ease;transform:none;box-shadow:none;opacity:0;transition-delay:0s\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:-50px;right:-50px;width:160px;height:160px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(196,154,60,.25);filter:blur(44px);opacity:0;transition:opacity .4s;pointer-events:none\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e\"></div><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.06),transparent);transition:background .3s\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e\"></div><div style=\"width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(196,154,60,.12);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,60,.22);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:18px;color:var(--gold);transition:transform .3s;transform:none\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z\"></path><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"></line><path d=\"M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0\"></path></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Fraunces&#x27;, serif;font-size:clamp(17px,1.2vw,21px);font-weight:400;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:-.2px\" class=\"jsx-a95eff13db39cd9e\">SOR Approval Workflow</h3><p style=\"font-size:clamp(13px,.85vw,15px);line-height:1.66;color:rgba(255,255,